name: Melffy Call to Play
effect: Your opponent cannot target Beast monsters you control with card effects. You can reveal 1 "Melffy" monster in your hand; Special Summon 1 "Melffy" monsters from your Deck with different names than the revealed monster. You can only use this effect of "Melffy Call to Play" once per turn.
